    "description": "<strong>Murder In Omar's Burger</strong>是一款沉浸式的<strong>2-4人游戏</strong>，背景设定在一家被谋杀之谜所困扰的汉堡店里。<br>在每场游戏中扮演侦探或杀手的角色，并与朋友们一起挑战你的侦探和潜行技能。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【侦探】</strong></h2>你正在调查一家汉堡店，以找到一个谋杀嫌疑人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209930/extras/8ec12420e12615217575c32b6b5d6bc5.poster.avif?t=1710367820\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209930/extras/8ec12420e12615217575c32b6b5d6bc5.webm?t=1710367820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209930/extras/8ec12420e12615217575c32b6b5d6bc5.mp4?t=1710367820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>找出并击毙员工中的杀手！<br></li><li>搜索证据，收集关于杀手的线索。<br></li><li>如果你击中了错的人，你就输了。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【杀手】</strong></h2>在侦探找出你是谁之前，隐藏证据并杀死他。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209930/extras/a3589aaab0ed52d349cbad471138c019.poster.avif?t=1710367820\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209930/extras/a3589aaab0ed52d349cbad471138c019.webm?t=1710367820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209930/extras/a3589aaab0ed52d349cbad471138c019.mp4?t=1710367820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在侦探出现之前隐藏所有证据。<br></li><li>保持工作以避免引起注意。<br></li><li>您可以利用断电来潜入侦探的后面。<br></li><li>留意进攻或者切换证据位置的机会。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【潜行】</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>杀手可以是餐厅员工中的任何人。<br></li><li>与其他员工一起工作以避免引起注意。<br></li><li>在断电期间，杀手可以自由移动，而侦探必须特别小心。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【玩法模式】</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>1 VS 1<br></li><li>2 VS 2</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【特点】</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>杀手的外表在每场游戏中都是随机生成的。</li></ul>",
